content: I've got some fresh produce like strawberries, blueberries, avocados, and some frozen chicken breasts and ground beef from Walmart. I also picked up a few bottles of wine, a 12-pack of soda, and some snacks like chips and popcorn. I'm planning to cook for myself, and I don't have any dietary restrictions. I'm open to any recipe suggestions, but I'd prefer something simple and quick for weekday lunches and dinners.
